  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Amebic liver abscess is the most frequent extra-intestinal form of the amoebiasis; actually
      the factors for predicting failure in the medical treatment are not clear. We conducted trial
      for determining the clinical value of paraclinical factor in this issue.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
